"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The DateFormatter and MonthLocator are used to format the x-axis as dates. However, when you use ax.set_xticks() and ax.set_xticklabels(), it overrides the DateFormatter and MonthLocator. This can lead to incorrect date formatting on the x-axis.\",\n  \"patch\": \"19,20d18\\n< ax.set_xticks(df.date.unique())\\n< ax.set_xticklabels(labels=df.date.unique(), rotation=45)\\n\"\n}"